---
import DocsLayout from "@/layouts/DocsLayout.astro";
import Button from "@/components/ui/Button.astro";
---
<DocsLayout
  title="Roadmap"
  description="A short pointer to the full roadmap — what's shipped, what's planned, and what's still a question."
>
  <p>
    CareerOS ships a complete daily pipeline today. Planned and research items
    are tracked honestly and never presented as done.
  </p>
  <ul>
    <li>
      <strong>Current</strong> — the full pipeline: multi-provider discovery,
      deterministic filtering and thresholding, the gate and evaluate reasoning
      steps, resume and cover generation with verification, application answers,
      the daily report, and the Google Sheet.
    </li>
    <li>
      <strong>Planned</strong> — direct-API providers for Greenhouse, Ashby,
      Lever, and Workday; incremental discovery; a scriptable config editor; and
      richer profile sections.
    </li>
    <li>
      <strong>Research</strong> — outcome tracking to calibrate scoring on real
      conversion data, and a SQLite store if the Sheet ever hits scaling limits.
    </li>
  </ul>
  <div class="not-prose mt-8">
    <Button href="/roadmap/">See the full roadmap and version history →</Button>
  </div>
</DocsLayout>
